The paper deals with a logical system and its decision procedure, which are typical topics in the area of logic (cs.LO). The use of global modalities and role hierarchies suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS). The mention of termination and efficiency in implementation suggests that the paper may also be relevant to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL).
